 of food kits Interested suppliers must submit their offer directly in the system as instructed in the solicitation document, following the instructions in the available user guide. In case you have never registered before, you can register a profile using the registration link shared via the procurement notice and following the instructions in guides available in the UNDP website: https://www.undp.org/procurement/business/resources-for-bidders . Do not create a new profile if you already have one. Use the forgotten password feature in case you do not remember the password or the username from previous registration. Search for the specific tender using search filters and subscribe to the tender in order to get notifications in case of amendments of the tender document. If you need support with the online system, you can contact the contact details of this tender as indicated in the solicitation document. This RFQ provides for engagement of the local/national companies due to the mandatory national certification requirements! UNDP OFFICE TAJIKISTAN PROCUREMENT UNIT Documents : Negotiation Document(s) (Before Accessing other negotiations Document(s), please click on this link ) United Nations Development Programme Twitter Facebook Youtube Instagram LinkedIn © 2026 United Nations Development Programme Terms of Use Twitter Facebook Youtube Instagram LinkedIn",
